 \"to\": 1719, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The Russian Foreign Ministry has condemned the IOC's suspension decision as \\\"wrongful, unjust and unacceptable.\\\"\", \"from\": 1721, \"to\": 1833, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1725, \"end\": 1749, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ministry_of_Foreign_Affairs_(Russia)\", \"score\": 0.9999999998756266, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Russian Foreign Ministry\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ministry_of_Foreign_Affairs_(Russia)\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ministry_of_Foreign_Affairs_(Russia)\"}, {\"begin\": 1768, \"end\": 1771, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 7.477818916218692e-23, \"text\": \"IOC\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"World No.\", \"from\": 1835, \"to\": 1844, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"10 Jabeur competed in the past three editions of the Olympics in London, Rio de Janeiro and Tokyo, but will not extend her streak to four in Paris.\", \"from\": 1845, \"to\": 1992, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1910, \"end\": 1916, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/London\", \"score\": 0.9999991602488878, \"rank\": 7.377282128736817e-07, \"text\": \"London\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/London\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/London\"}, {\"begin\": 1918, \"end\": 1932, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rio_de_Janeiro\", \"score\": 0.9999999999993179, \"rank\": 5.653489792355909e-13, \"text\": \"Rio de Janeiro\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\", \"Q3957\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rio_de_Janeiro\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rio_de_Janeiro\"}, {\"begin\": 1937, \"end\": 1942, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo_b